      • createBuffer

        @ReflectionExplicit
public static final TransferBuffer createBuffer(java.io.InputStream stream)
                                                             throws Transfer.TransferOperationException
        Wraps input stream. Since the general contract of a buffer class requires that contents of a buffer were immediately available this InputStream are read into collector or any special holder. An exception that may rise while reading an InputStream is throwed from this method. In any case InputStream will be closed on exit from this method!
